the new technology to be used at the new plants 
there is some high risk associated with getting the technology 
to work he said 
peach also questioned the energy departments cost calculations 
for the 18 different options it considered he said the department 
had taken cost estimates for fullsized reactors and scaled them 
down for use in figuring the cost of smaller reactors 
