<TEXT>
a gleaming american airlines dc10 taxied down 
the runway for takeoff 10 years ago thursday lifting off into a 
nightmarish niche in us aviation history 
flight 191 was over in seconds the jetliner and its inhabitants 
instantly reduced to scattered debris in what remains the nations 
worst air crash 
the plane lost an engine on takeoff banked sideways out of 
control and slammed into a nearby field exploding into a jetfuel 
inferno all 258 passengers and 13 crew members died as well as 
two people on the ground 
just the sound of a jet it just brings it back every time i 
