and lithuania 
many soviet citizens frustrated by empty stores and unkept 
promises to fill them have put their faith in the congress 
pravda the communist party newspaper quoted one on wednesday 
as saying he hoped it would make our life our country such that 
you can once again say without blushing i am a citizen of the 
soviet union 
tass quoted vitautas ramanauskas a lithuanian deputy as 
