prevent defense companies with more than 10 million in contracts 
from hiring senior defense personnel for two years after those 
officials leave government service 
the lawmakers defined senior officials as those receiving no 
less than 68700 a year and specifically mentioned the defense 
secretary general counsel and the services secretary and chief of 
staff 
in all there are 1580 civilians and 1073 general officers who 
