1987 data the latest figures available 39 percent of former 
senior pentagon officials worked on the same contract for a defense 
company that they had handled while at the pentagon 
the gao reported that about 70 percent of former defense 
officials violate the law by failing to report their new jobs with 
defense contractors 
the question before us today is whether the american people 
will be asked to throw up their hands and resign themselves to 
having their chicken coops guarded by some very hungry foxes 
aucoin said at a news conference 
bennett called the legislation a simple bill that for two 
years would prevent somebody in a highranking position from 
