federal home loan bank board demonstrates the anger felt by 
managers of healthy sampls who blame sloppy or dishonest rivals for 
the present crisis in the fund that insures customers deposits 
great western the nations thirdbiggest thrift stands to lose 
20 million this year because of the bank board ruling that amount 
is the difference in the cost of coverage by the federal savings amp 
loan insurance corp and the federal deposit insurance corp the 
fund for banks 
